com.github.wuic.engine
Class EngineOutputManager

java.lang.Object
  com.github.wuic.engine.EngineOutputManager

public final class EngineOutputManager
extends Object

This class is in charge to provides directory where the engines must generate their files.

Actually, this directory is located in the temporary directory of the file system and in a directory name 'wuic' (BASE_WORKING_NAME). The manager also clears the directories tree when it is created.
